      <h2 class="title-purple" id="about-title">Our origin story</h2>
      <p>Andy, a business leader and organizational psychologist, & Ali, a leadership & strategy specialist, met studying applied neuroscience. Over many heated discussions, they formed a view that the prevailing popular models for team leadership were fundamentally flawed.</p>

      <p><strong>The existing team models were based on outmoded MBA thinking and far away from what the neuroscience was teaching them about what really drives high performance.</strong></p>

      <p>This was so frustrating to us. We both felt passionately that better teams lead to better times and a better world. <strong>Great outcomes happen in eco systems and teams, not through individuals.</strong> All of the solutions to the big and small, to the fun, to the sports, to the commercial – depend ultimately on high performing teams.</p>
